<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>COME LET US BUILT</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa leh Agam dingin,
 Nasem dingin hung kisau;
 Nasep a hun tai na gamsung ah,
 Hung halhdawk inla, entie;
 Na gamsung kulhpi a chim zotai,
 Kihechien in enin.
 &quot;Hung halhdawk in, (3)
 Kingaihtuoh in!&quot; Lalpa'n A tii.

[V2]
 2. Nehemia Persia leng khawn pie'n,
 A na pang ta-mahlele;
 Jerusalem siet a het phetin,
 A lungkham mah mah ta a;
 A umna mun luite chuh nusie'n,
 Siempha di'n a chieh tai.

[V3]
 3. Nungak, tangval, nupi, upa,
 Na gamsung lungsiet lo maw?
 Na kulhpi bang dettak maite chuh,
 Setan in phie ding ahi;
 Hung halhdawk inla, vak enviel tie,
 Nehemia ngaihtuoh in.

[V4]
 4. Nehemia mi ginum tak chuh,
 Sanballat leh Tobiah te'n;
 Muhsit bawlin nuihsan mahleu le,
 A lung adawng diek ngei puoi;
 Mite'n hun musit ta mahleu le,
 Kipakin sem zelin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>301</hymn_number>
</song>